snippet.textDisplay:
You people want to hear some guy who is no more qualified than yourself basically sell you a product he knows nothing about? He knows nothing about 99% of what he unboxes. Then, you want him to make your opinions for you? Every comment I see is people asking for him to relate his opinion.. when it’s clear he has no idea about anything to do with the product.

I have no idea why people can’t form their own opinions and do so through their own thinking minds. People are so desperate for others to think and act for them. Do yourself a favor, watch something that educates vs something designed to push you away from the experience at hand.
